result.execSummary:
The defendant Sealena B. Booker was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Sealena B. Booker is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Sealena B. Booker was found guilty of Disorderly Conduct [Modifiers: Repeater, Use of a Dangerous Weapon, Domestic Abuse], a class B misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 947.01(1).
